    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! It truly breaks my heart to even think about parting with this absolute gem, but it\u2019s time for her to find a new home where she\u2019ll be just as pampered. This beauty is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, she looks and drives just like the day she rolled off the lot. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping her tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washing her every single weekend. You won't find a single speck of dust out of place, and that 'new car' feeling is still very much alive. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved with every mile, come by for a chat and a look\u2014I promise you\u2019ll fall in love just like I did!",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
