    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a masterpiece of automotive poetry. This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a time capsule that captures the golden age of the open road. Every curve of its hand-polished silhouette whispers stories of moonlit coastal drives and sun-drenched mountain passes. The cabin greets you with the rich, intoxicating scent of heritage leather, preserved as if time itself stood still. To drive it is to command a symphony of precision and grace, a mechanical soul that beats in perfect rhythm with your own. This is more than a purchase; it\u2019s an inheritance of style, a rare jewel for the discerning soul who understands that true beauty is eternal.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
