    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an unparalleled example of automotive excellence, this vehicle arrives in absolute showroom condition. Meticulously curated and maintained to the highest standards, it features a flawless exterior finish complemented by a pristine, smoke-free interior that retains its original luster. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure peak performance, offering the next owner a seamless blend of luxury and reliability. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that truly defies its age, representing the pinnacle of its class in both aesthetic appeal and mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 48900.0,
