    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lover! Thanks for stopping by to take a look at my absolute pride and joy. I\u2019ve spent more Sunday mornings than I can count polishing this beauty, and it truly shows\u2014she\u2019s in stunning, showroom-ready shape. Driving this feels like stepping back in time to the day it was first delivered; the interior still has that fresh feel and the engine purrs like a kitten. It\u2019s been garage-kept and treated like a member of the family, so you\u2019re getting a real gem here. I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come on over, let's chat cars, and you can see for yourself just how special this one is!",
      "price": 48900.0,
